# Cloudflare Pages rewrites (publish root = static/).
# The HTML references assets as /static/*; rewrite those to the published root so they
# resolve without editing every <script>/<link>. A genuinely missing file still 404s
# (the rewrite target won't exist), so this does not mask broken assets.
/static/* /:splat 200
# NOTE: /player is intentionally NOT redirected here. Cloudflare serves it natively via
# clean URLs (/player -> player.html); adding an explicit /player -> /player.html rule
# collides with that and causes a /player -> /player redirect loop. (Dev: Flask serves /player.)
